{"tid":773872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偉業街18歲仔 更衣室偷拍男子被捕","createTime":"2018-08-10T01:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T03:05:41.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e68eb0ac0b16a14ce5e4059025c62daa50f77330","tid":773872,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"一名32歲男子，昨晚11時許在牛頭角偉業街報案，指一名37歲男事主早前在偉業街一更衣室內，懷疑被一名18歲姓羅男子用手機偷拍。警方接報到場，並撿獲一部手機，經初步調查後，案件列有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦，羅男涉案被捕，案件交由秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180810/58544868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180810%2F58544868&d=HmHxKdJjUk%2BEk7gZk2GpEU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=36eec0bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180810%2F58544868&h=23d5b12d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180810/58544868</a>"},{"pid":"a3a18673e5e5c2bf4ce9d39bb9cf20a8823966a2","tid":773872,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"究竟「不誠實意圖而取用電腦」其實係包乜"},{"pid":"8c6bde401eb4dc9d6d6fc1ad3be57a96e46d243e","tid":773872,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"以後偷拍記得用菲林機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74f52b67cda41f649dc13e723bc283987bc3e74","tid":773872,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a18673e5e5c2bf4ce9d39bb9cf20a8823966a2","tid":773872,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"究竟「不誠實意圖而取用電腦」其實係包乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:45:37.000Z","msg":"所有電子野佢話包就包架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9070e58bc8a8a3c33cdcdfa8a9d94583ab5dd832","tid":773872,"uid":25099,"li